icontrol

Class IcontrolView.MyTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • icontrol.IcontrolView.MyTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
    Enclosing class:
    IcontrolView

    private class IcontrolView.MyTableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
    Define a new TableModel as anonymous inner class. Note that getColumnClass needs access to the Table (m_jTab) because it is still called by JTable:getTableCellEditorComponent although methods JTable:getCellEditor() and JTable:getCellRenderer are overridden.

    The text for the Headers of the Table is defined here.

    Note that by selecting 2 or 3 as return value in getColumnCount it is possible to show the Tooltips as part of the Table.
